8548-9 |lccn=2006050263 |oclc=71223542 |ref=Humes 2007|title-link=Monkey Girl: Evolution, Education, Religion, and the Battle for America's Soul }}\n* {{cite book |last=Johnson |first=Phillip E. |authorlink=Phillip E. Johnson |year=1991 |title=Darwin on Trial |location=Washington, D.C. |publisher=[[Regnery Publishing|Regnery Gateway]] |isbn=978-0-8952-6535-7 |lccn=90026218 |oclc=22906277 |ref=Johnson 1991|title-link=Darwin on Trial }}\n* {{cite book |last=Johnson |first=Phillip E. |year=1995 |title=Reason in the Balance: The Case Against Naturalism in Science, Law & Education |location=Downers Grove, IL |publisher=InterVarsity Press |isbn=978-0-830-81610-1 |lccn=95012620 |oclc=32384818 |ref=Johnson 1995 |url=https://archive.org/details/reasoninbalancec00john }}\n* {{cite book |last=Johnson |first=Phillip E. |year=1997 |title=Defeating Darwinism by Opening Minds |location=Downers Grove, Ill. |publisher=InterVarsity Press |isbn=978-0-8308-1360-5 |lccn=97012916 |oclc=36621960 |ref=Johnson 1997 |url=https://archive.org/details/defeatingdarwini00john_0 }}\n* {{cite book |last=Johnson |first=Phillip E. |year=2000 |title=The Wedge of Truth: Splitting the Foundations of Naturalism |url=https://archive.org/details/wedgeoftruthspli0000john |url-access=registration |location=Downers Grove, Ill. |publisher=InterVarsity Press |isbn=978-0-8308-2267-6 |lccn=00039586 |oclc=43903750 |ref=Johnson 2000}}\n* {{cite book |last=Meyer |first=Stephen C. |authorlink=Stephen C. Meyer |year=2009 |title=Signature in the Cell |edition=1st |location=New York |publisher=[[HarperCollins|HarperOne]] |isbn=978-0-06-147278-7 |lccn=2008051773 |oclc=232978147 |ref=Meyer 2009|title-link=Signature in the Cell }}\n* {{cite book |last=Numbers |first=Ronald L. |authorlink=Ronald L. Numbers |year=2006 |origyear=Originally published 1992 as ''The Creationists: The Evolution of Scientific Creationism''; New York: [[Alfred A. Knopf]] |title=The Creationists: From Scientific Creationism to Intelligent Design |ed