ngle to participate. Also featured in \"Gonna Jump\".\n|-\n|}\n\n==== Albums ====\n''Song participiations aside from single title track recordings:''\n\n* ''[[Koko ni Ita Koto]]'' (2011), 4 songs\n* ''[[1830m]]'' (2012), 2 songs\n* ''[[Tsugi no Ashiato]]'' (2014), 4 songs\n* ''[[Koko ga Rhodes da, Koko de Tobe!]]'' (2015), 2 songs\n\n==== Team Surprise ====\nShe participated in the first two incarnations of Team Surprise, a subunit formed for a Pachinko machine campaign, but was not selected for the third:\n* {{Nihongo|Suteki na Sankaku Kankei|\u7d20\u6575\u306a\u4e09\u89d2\u95a2\u4fc2}}\n* {{Nihongo|Namida ni Shizumu Taiyou|\u6d99\u306b\u6c88\u3080\u592a\u967d}}\n* {{Nihongo|Kimi ga Omotteru yori|\u30ad\u30df\u304c\u601d\u3063\u3066\u308b\u3088\u308a}}\n* {{Nihongo|Megami wa Doko de Hohoemu?|\u5973\u795e\u306f\u3069\u3053\u3067\u5fae\u7b11\u3080\uff1f}}\n\n==== Other singles participation ====\n* \"{{Nihongo|Dareka no Tame Ni|\u8ab0\u304b\u306e\u305f\u3081\u306b}} - What can I do for someone?\" (2011)\n* \"{{Nihongo|Koi no Onawa|\u604b\u306e\u304a\u7e04}}\" (2011)\n* \"{{Nihongo|Tenohira ga Kataru Koto| \u638c\u304c\u8a9e\u308b\u3053\u3068}}\" (2013)\n* \"Enjoy your life!\" (2013), on [[Tomomi Kasai]]'s second single release, \"Mine\"\n* \"{{Nihongo|Datte, Ame Janai?|\u3060\u3063\u3066\u3001\u96e8\u3058\u3083\u306a\u3044 }}\", on [[Love Crescendo]] first single release \"{{Nihongo|Koppu no Naka no Komorebi|\u30b3\u30c3\u30d7\u306e\u4e2d\u306e\u6728\u6f0f\u308c\u65e5}}\"\n\n=== SKE48 ===\n\n==== Main singles ====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! data-sort-type=\"number\" | No. <!--- SKE48 major single number ---->\n! style=\"width:150px;\"| Title <!--- title of main single ---->\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes <!--- add other tracks that she participated in, references ---->\n|-\n| 2014\n| 15\n| \"[[Bukiy\u014d Taiy\u014d]]\"\n| A-side\n| Also appeared in \"Houkago Race\" with Team S\n|-\n| 2015\n| 16\n| \"[[12 Gatsu no Kangaroo]]\"\n| A-sid